oducts as well as acoustical ceiling wall and structural solutions and sells suspension system products it sells its commercial ceiling materials and accessories to resale distributors and ceiling system contractors and residential ceiling products to wholesalers and retailers including large home centers the company was incorporated in  and is headquartered in lancaster pennsylvania  columbia avenuelancaster pa united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwarmstrongceilingscom key executives for armstrong world industries inc mr victor d grizzle chief executive officer president and director age  total annual compensation k mr brian l macneal chief financial officer and senior vice president age  total annual compensation k mr mark a hershey chief compliance officer senior vice president general counsel and secretary age  total annual compensation m mr david s cookson senior vice president of americas age  total annual compensation k ms ellen r romano senior vice president of human resources age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  armstrong world industries inc key developments armstrong world industries to provide ceiling solutions for the metropolitan transportation authoritys east side access megaproject may   armstrong world industries inc announced it was selected to provide ceiling solutions for the metropolitan transportation authoritys east side access megaproject the transportation construction project underway in the united states that will connect the long island rail road lirr to a new concourse underneath grand central terminal armstrong was chosen for its broad product portfolio design services construction expertise and technical competencies a combination unmatched in the ceilings industry this marks the third in a series of large transportation projects in manhattan for which armstrong ceiling solutions were recently specified the first fulton center the gateway to lower manhattan opened in  and the second south ferry statio