during normal operation when the mechanical seal wears out it can be replaced in less than ve minutes which reduces on site labor costs for contractorsthe highly efficient dry motor design and hydraulics make the e series circulator more efficient than other fixed speed pumps in its class this excellent wiretowater efficiency leads to energy savings that building owners will appreciatethe compact size of e series circulators makes them easy to install even in con ned spaces the minimized angeto ange dimensions combined with the armstrong o ering of crossreferenced spool pieces make it easy for contractors to upgrade an existing circulator with an e series circulator without making changes to the installed piping  if you have any questions please give us a call at  or email us your request salesnationalpumpsupplycom featured items newest items bestselling alphabetical a to z alphabetical z to a avg customer review price low to high price high to low sort by  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong armflo e circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong e cast iron armflo pump  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong e armflo pump cast iron  add to cart  armstrong armflo e cast iron pump  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong armflo e circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong e armflo pump cast iron  add to cart  armstrong e armflo pump cast iron  add to cart  armstrong eb bronze armflo circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating pump  add to cart  armstrong e armflo pump cast iron  add to cart  armstrong e armflo pump cast iron  add to cart  armstrong e cast iron armflo pump  add to cart  armstrong cast iron pump armflo e  add to cart  armstrong eb armflo bronze circulating 